rComments: I liked this course and professor Beghtol. She was not everyone's cup of tea for sure, but she had a quality of a solid professional, though the subject certainly was a bit boring and perhaps not so useful in this new information era.

Very nice person if you take the opportunity to interact with her.  Teaches subjects which few people wish to learn at this point in history, but teaches them with genuinely expert knowledge of her fields.
Great prof - wity and sharp.  Does not suffer fools gladly, actually, not at all
